# Libraries

Below are the libraries that need to be loaded in order to run the code in this RMarkdown file.

```{r, include =F}
library(tidyverse)
library(stats)
library(emmeans)
library(kableExtra)
library(Rmisc)
library(car)
library(reshape2)
library(lme4)
library(lmerTest)
library(sjPlot)
library(pwr)
library(rstatix)
```

